{"componentChunkName":"component---src-containers-post-layout-tsx","path":"/ray-tracing-5","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3>그림자</h3>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/1zpp112rgs6ow1n/shadow_principle.jpg?raw=1\" width=\"50%\">\n</center>\n<p>그림자는 물체와 광원 사이에 다른 물체가 있어 빛을 가로막거나 빛의 일부만 도달했을 때 생깁니다. 즉, 물체와 광원 사이에 다른 물체가 있는지, 있다면 얼마만큼의 빛을 가로막고 통과시키는지 알 수 있다면 그림자를 구현할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h3>Shadow ray</h3>\n<p>색을 구하고자 하는 물체 표면의 한 점을 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span>, 광원을 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">L</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span></span></span></span> 이라고 하겠습니다. <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 에 닿는 빛의 방향 벡터는 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mover accent=\"true\"><mrow><mi>L</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\overline{LP}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8833300000000001em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833300000000001em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.80333em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 라 할 수 있습니다. 만약 직선 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mover accent=\"true\"><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>L</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\overline{PL}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8833300000000001em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833300000000001em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.80333em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 사이에 다른 물체가 있다면 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 에 그림자가 생긴다고 판정할 수 있습니다. 물체가 있다고 판단하는 것은 {% post_link ray-tracing-object-intersect intersection %}파트에서 이미 살펴본 바 있습니다.</p>\n<p>카메라의 위치를 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>e</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">e</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span></span></span></span>, 카메라에서 2차원 평면의 픽셀을 향하는 벡터를 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">d</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">d</span></span></span></span> 라 할 때 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>e</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mi>d</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">ray = e +td</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">d</span></span></span></span> 와 같이 썼습니다.</p>\n<p>그림자의 경우 출발점 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 와, 광원을 향하는 벡터 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mover accent=\"true\"><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>L</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\overline{PL}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8833300000000001em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833300000000001em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.80333em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 를 정규화한 벡터 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">d</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">d</span></span></span></span> 를 이용해 다음과 같이 shadow ray 를 쓸 수 있습니다.</p>\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>h</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>w</mi><mtext> </mtext><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>P</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mi>d</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">shadow\\text{ }ray = P + td</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">h</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">d</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">o</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02691em;\">w</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\"> </span></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.76666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">d</span></span></span></span></span>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/2ojvdom9094hinn/shadow_ray_explain.jpg?raw=1\" width=\"60%\">\n</center>\n<p>공간안의 모든 물체에 대해서 shadow ray 와의 부딪힘 여부를 판단하고 만약 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.61508em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span></span> 가 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 와 광원과의 거리인 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>∥</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>L</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"true\">‾</mo></mover><mo>∥</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\parallel \\overline{PL} \\parallel</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∥</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.13333em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord overline\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8833300000000001em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.80333em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"overline-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∥</span></span></span></span> 보다 작은 양수라면 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 와 광원사이에 물체가 있다고 할 수 있습니다. 만약 물체가 투명도 속성을 가지고 있지 않다면 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 의 색을 단순히 검은색으로 지정하고, 투명도가 있다면 이를 반영해 색을 계산합니다. 예를 들어 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 와 광원 사이에 위치한 물체 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span> 의 투명도가 20% 라면 phong reflection 에 의해 계산한 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 의 RGB 벡터 각각의 요소에 0.2 를 곱해줍니다.</p>\n<p>만약 여러 물체가 shadow ray 와 부딪힌다면 물체의 투명도들을 모두 곱한 결과를 이용할 수 있습니다. 예를 들어 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 와 광원 사이에 물체 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span>, <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span></span></span></span> 가 있고 각각의 투명도가 0.2, 0.1 이라면 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0.2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.02</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0.2 \\times 0.1 = 0.02</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span> 를 RGB 벡터의 각각의 요소에 곱한 결과가 점 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 의 색이 됩니다. shadow ray 를 이용해 그림자가 표현된 이미지를 렌더해 보겠습니다.</p>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/briqph2jpr4nxvk/shadow_noise.png?raw=1\" width=\"60%\">\n</center>\n<p>평면에 구의 그림자가 표현되었지만 렌더된 결과에 전체적으로 노이즈가 있습니다. 물체 표면의 점 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 가 의도한 정확한 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 의 좌표가 아니기 때문입니다. 부동소수점의 오차로 인해 실제 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 의 좌표는 정확히 물체 위에 있지 않습니다.</p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h3>Bias 의 필요성</h3>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/19p3xk7deu93pk0/shadow_bias_explain.jpg?raw=1\" width=\"60%\">\n</center>\n<p>위 그림과 같이 물체 위의 점 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 가 물체의 표면보다 아주 조금 아래에 있다면 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 에서 출발해 광원을 향하는 shadow ray 는 물체 자기 자신과 부딪힙니다. 이전의 렌더 결과에서 노이즈가 발생한 이유가 바로 이것 때문입니다.\n물체 위의 점 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 를 물체 표면 조금 위의 위치로 이동시키면 이를 해결할 수 있습니다. 이동방향은 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 에서의 법선벡터이고 이동시킨 점을 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>P</mi><mo mathvariant=\"normal\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">′</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>P</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>s</mi><mtext> </mtext><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P&#x27; = P + Bias\\text{ }n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.751892em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.751892em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.76666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\"> </span></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 와 같이 쓸 수 있습니다. 이 때 Bias 는 법선벡터 방향으로의 거리이고 0.0001 과 같이 아주 작은 값으로 설정합니다. Bias 가 적용된 결과를 렌더해 보겠습니다.</p>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/s7e60inc27l5q7u/shadow_biased.png?raw=1\" width=\"60%\">\n</center>","frontmatter":{"date":null,"slug":"/ray-tracing-5","title":"레이 트레이싱 (5) 그림자","tags":["그래픽스","레이 트레이싱"],"category":["그래픽스"],"description":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ray-tracing-5","categories":[{"category":"선형대수학","count":26,"href":"/category/선형대수학"},{"category":"그래픽스","count":12,"href":"/category/그래픽스"},{"category":"병렬 프로그래밍","count":3,"href":"/category/병렬 프로그래밍"},{"category":"최적화 문제","count":3,"href":"/category/최적화 문제"},{"category":"알고리즘","count":2,"href":"/category/알고리즘"},{"category":"미적분","count":2,"href":"/category/미적분"}],"tags":[{"tag":"코딩 더 매트릭스","count":24,"href":"/tag/코딩 더 매트릭스"},{"tag":"python","count":24,"href":"/tag/python"},{"tag":"그래픽스","count":7,"href":"/tag/그래픽스"},{"tag":"레이 트레이싱","count":5,"href":"/tag/레이 트레이싱"},{"tag":"알고리즘","count":4,"href":"/tag/알고리즘"},{"tag":"OpenCL","count":3,"href":"/tag/OpenCL"},{"tag":"C","count":3,"href":"/tag/C"},{"tag":"회전","count":3,"href":"/tag/회전"},{"tag":"행렬","count":2,"href":"/tag/